<p><strong>Skills</strong> Intimidation +2</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> any one language (usually Common)</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/2 (100 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Pack Tactics.</em></strong> The thug has advantage on an attack roll against a creature if at least one of the thug’s allies is within 5 ft. of the creature and the ally isn’t incapacitated.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The thug makes two melee attacks.</p>

<p><strong><em>Mace.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) bludgeoning damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Heavy Crossbow.</em></strong> Ranged Weapon Attack: +2 to hit, range 100/400 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d10) piercing damage.</p>

